{
  "stem": "17001.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 69.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my grandparents had a-- a machine that was-- was making the wheat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You needed a big, big heavy leather to go around the wheel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, from that leather, he was using it for the sole, to make the shoe sole.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was making shoes for my cousins and many of the family members from his side of the family, because my mother family were most of them in the United State, except one of her younger sister, who was in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the rest of the sisters they-- and brothers, they were all in United State.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mandok was a fairly middle-sized city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had like mayor's building.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had like other big official's building, like some soldiers who examining the tobacco-- I mean, I can't translate-- but who were strictly out for the unofficial-- the bootlegging whiskey, and also for the tobacco.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was another building, the gendarmes, the police department, so I would say that it was a fairly middle-class--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The largest was Kisvarda.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which was about 18 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, Kisvarda was the one where I was going to middle class school, [NON-ENGLISH], a gymnasium, whatever you want to call it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my brother, my older brother was born in 1923.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Philip.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he used to go to yeshiva until the situation changed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then my parents arranged for him to become apprentice at a tailor place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, he was working three years without any pay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after that, he had to have a release, a paper, and make a test front of a committee in order to get the-- sort of like a diploma, that he successfully finished the-- the trade.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
